我好嬲，亦都好想喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月12日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月1日<br />\n香港警察面對手無寸鐵既示威者亂棍打人，窮追猛打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqbm0Uy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpqbm0Uy.gif&h=0d6106c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：（2019年6月12日）<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=3e2eafbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=7cbc9606\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=3a7d9ef8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=41a2c472\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=57777697\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=0c1ed081\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a>"},{"pid":"80919785df297f9fdfa85a65f64e448685dd36ea","tid":1275652,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:43:25.000Z","msg":"長輩圖材料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1275207/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1275207/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7158f1e64e0dae9f26411e1173e9ed2baef1acf3","tid":1275652,"uid":266706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2866a8155e631a860b0dec14038563133a264b0f","tid":1275652,"uid":115136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:45:25.000Z","msg":"[文宣-7.1衝立會] 給父母的信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中產buy"},{"pid":"932a79c62cedc2b2f89c765d1796ce9c0942e4da","tid":1275652,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:45:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔該入嚟幫手推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【廣傳】所有出現過喺現場嘅義士，見到呢個post 即刻更改Facebook私隱設定，尤其係相！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275626</a></span>"},{"pid":"e333b3f2ee690bf34893d6b699a65872a2f0e9a9","tid":1275652,"uid":6629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:47:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23b0fade5c8f66629e8a26d9112b2c0f10e40112","tid":1275652,"uid":86602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:48:36.000Z","msg":"一定要提第4點！話林鄭冷血<br />\n不回應年輕人因反送中自殺<br />\n枉為母親！愧對烈士家屬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林奠回應三個年輕人因反送中自殺既問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275554</a>"},{"pid":"e9fa02ffee789d88a691cb